==Reception==
{{expand section|date=June 2023}}
The game received fairly positive reviews from critics. The game received praise for its graphics and sound, as well as its controls and platforming design, but the gameplay received some criticism, which was viewed as a bit repetitive and at times even frustrating.<ref>[http://www.gamefreaks365.com/review.php?artid=622 Gamefreaks] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211082903/http://www.gamefreaks365.com/review.php?artid=622 |date=February 11, 2009 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.gamefaqs.com/console/a2600/review/R18031.html Gamefaqs]</ref><ref>[http://www.atarihq.com/reviews/2600/adventures_of_tron.html Atari HQ]</ref><ref>[http://abscape.org/legeek/r_advtron.htm AB Scape]</ref>

